Package com.example.demo.ui.page

Class SettingPage

java.lang.Object
com.example.demo.ui.page.SettingPage
public class SettingPage extends Object
Represents the settings page in the application. This class provides methods to initialize and display the settings page, allowing users to mute or unmute music and sound effects.
